WikiRAG v2.4.0 - VERSIONC3
============================

Release Date: 2025-02-01
Codename: "Mental Theater"

This release includes:

## Core Features
- Multi-strategy RAG system (BM25, FAISS, GraphRAG, Hybrid)
- Memory-optimized BM25 with lazy loading
- Smart Router with direct execution

## Agent System
- Claude-style agent architecture (Thinker, Planner, Executor, Verifier)
- ReAct agent with tool integration
- Strategic Agent for task decomposition

## New in v2.4.0
- Mental Theater: 6-profile deliberation system
  - Luz (Logic), Sombra (Risk), Luna (Context)
  - Agua (Adaptation), Fuego (Action), Viento (Alternatives)
- Event-based Queue System (inbox/processing/archive)
- Multi-channel Messaging (Telegram, Webhooks)
- SmartToolDecider with automatic risk blocking

## Requirements
- Python 3.9+
- llama.cpp with compatible GGUF model
- macOS/Linux

## Quick Start
1. Copy to ~/wikirag/
2. Create virtual environment: python -m venv venv
3. Install dependencies: pip install -r requirements.txt
4. Configure config/mcp_config.json
5. Run: ./start.sh

